short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is the helper of enrolling class in IUB

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
IUBClassHelper is an extension for helping students in IUB enroll class.

User can search the class in iGPS and use this extension to easily search the professor's ratings in RateMyProfessor and the history of grades of this course with only one-click action.
